A woman in Khaldeh screams: & quot;
04 Nov 2019, 11:27 by Lebanon 24
A woman in Khaldeh was in urgent need of traffic because her mother was in hospital, she said. The young woman appeared in the video, removing obstacles and stones from the middle of the road and shouting: "I want my mother to be sick in the hospital ... my mother is dead." The Sheikh said: "You Chili stones and I will return their response and we will open the way."
